page.title: 09Home Life, Murroes
page.content: My name is Jimmy and I am nine years old. I live with my family - Mum, Dad and sister Trudy who is fifteen. At school I am in class P.5 and I am not very fast at doing my maths. I am also a little bit slow at doing some of my other work. My hobby is playing the bagpipes, and sometimes I am good at playing them. Recently I was playing at a competition and came in second. I like to play on my bike, and make big jumps so that I can go over them on my{BMX bike.} Sometimes I hurt myself when I am doing this, but it is good fun just the same. My sister's hobby is horse riding.
